speech data.

You may use, modify, and share this code for non-commercial research,
evaluation, and reproducibility. You may not use this code or generated
artifacts to build, train, or deploy systems intended to commit fraud,
impersonation, social engineering, or other harmful activity.

Full benchmark audio, private reference voices, model checkpoints, API keys,
and provider response logs are not covered by this code release unless
